<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Scholarship Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        
        .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .option {
            flex: 1 1 45%;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .option:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .option {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Scholarship Options</h1>
        <div class="options">
            <div class="option" onclick="window.location.href='/EducationLoans'">
                <h2>Education Loan Guidance</h2>
                <p>Get advice on education loans.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="option" onclick="window.location.href='/scholarshipsc'">
                <h2>Government and Other Scholarships</h2>
                <p>Explore available scholarships.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="option" onclick="window.location.href='/education'">
                <h2> Education Loan </h2>
                <p>there are some Contect Number of Bank Loan Head officer that may help you to provide education loan</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
